betterquesting:10.name:8: A Mothership to the T9 system
betterquesting:10.desc:8:
There is one last star system to conquer. You need one final rocket to get there. A big one. So big in fact you should build it in space. Make a shuttle rocket to get up there and build the mothership (similar to how you build a space station).

There are new ore veins on the T9 planets. In particular you should look for Tengam on Seth. You will need that for UEV.
